	* elmo.el (elmo-folder-clear): Reconstruct msgdb if
	elmo-msgdb-convert-type is `sync'.

	* elmo-vars.el (elmo-msgdb-default-type): Added `standard'.
	(elmo-msgdb-convert-type): New user option.

