	* elmo-multi.el: Rewrite with luna.

	* elmo-vars.el (elmo-use-killed-list): Abolish.
	All other related portions are changed.
	(elmo-filename-replace-string-alist): Renamed from
	elmo-msgid-replace-string-alist.

