	* elmo.el: New file.

	* elmo2.el: Renamed to elmo.el.


2001-02-01  OKAZAKI Tetsurou  <okazaki@be.to>

	* elmo-cache.el (elmo-cache-expire-by-size): Count
	a disk usage for a cache file entry in KB even when
	its kind is a directory.

