	(elmo-imap4-nil): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-atom): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-quoted): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-literal-subr): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-literal): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-buffer-literal): Ditto.
	(elmo-imap4-string-subr): Ditto.
